App with a bot <br>
App Name: Nolwazi ("Mother of Knowledge")

Industry : Personal finance:

Target users: Learners, Students, Young Professionals, Job seekers, State dependants and general users with interest in engaging with a bot
on financial matters <br>
Aims: <br>
1. Giving personal financial advice to various users in SA. <br>
2. Inform the public <br>
3. Educate the public <br>
4. Ease of making financial decisions at a personal  level "on one's own". 
